Symbol.Script_1D:
! ui_appearance_type_m = 0 MEP objects visualization tab ! ui_appearance_type_m = 2 Appliance objects visualization tab
! iObjectType values
BASIN_NORMAL = 10 BASIN_DOUBLE = 11 BASIN_CORNER = 12 BASIN_HANDICAP = 13 BASIN_BUILTINCIRCLE = 14 BASIN_BUILTINELLIP = 15 BASIN_BUILTINMULTI = 16
SHOWER_RECT = 20 SHOWER_CORNER = 21 SHOWER_CORNERCURVED = 22 SHOWER_CABIN = 23
BATHTUB_NORMAL = 30 BATHTUB_CORNER = 31 BATHTUB_TRAPEZOID = 32 BATHTUB_FREESTANDING = 33
WC_TANK = 40 WC_NOTANK = 41 WC_CORNERTANK = 42 SQUATTING_TOILET = 43
BIDET = 50
DRINKING_FOUNTAIN_NORMAL = 60 DRINKING_FOUNTAIN_COVERED = 61 DRINKING_FOUNTAIN_STANDING = 62
JACUZZI_ROUND = 70 JACUZZI_SQUARE = 71
URINAL_NORMAL = 80 URINAL_CORNER = 81 URINAL_WITHFLUSH = 82 URINAL_04 = 83
MOP_SINK = 90 SINK_BELFAST = 91 SINK_CORNER = 92 SINK_GENERAL = 93
TAP = 100 SHOWER_TAP = 101
Symbol.Script_UI:
!---------- MEP objects visualization tab ----------- pageStartY = 5
if ui_appearance_type_m = 0 then
UI_SEPARATOR 222, pageStartY - 1, 222, pageStartY + 230
add_Y = 24
x1 = 5 x2 = x1 + 30 x3 = x2 + 150 x4 = x1 + 117 x5 = x3 + 27 x6 = x2 + 27 y = pageStartY - 3
UI_STYLE 0,1 UI_OUTFIELD `2D-отображение`, x1, y, x3-x2,18 ! --- Plan Symbol --- UI_STYLE 0, 0 y = y + add_Y
cx = 90 IF bEnable2dDetail THEN if iObjectType = SINK_BELFAST | iObjectType = SINK_CORNER | iObjectType = SINK_GENERAL then ui_outfield `Тип Символа Мойки`, x1, y, x4-x1-1, 15 ui_infield{3} "SinkSymbol", x4, y-4, cx, 20, 8, "", 2, 1, -x3-1, 20, -x3-1, 20, "", `Детали Слива`, `Детали Слива`, "", `Детальный`, `Детальный`, "", `Простой`, `Простой` y = y + add_Y else if iObjectType <> TAP & iObjectType <> SHOWER_TAP then ui_outfield `2D-детализация`, x1, y, x4-x1-1, 15
dim stDetail2d[]
call "2dDetailLevel" parameters all, returned_parameters stDetail2d
ui_infield{3} "gs_detlevel_2D_m", x4, y-4, cx, 20, 8, "", 2, 1, -x3-1, 20, -x3-1, 20, "", stDetail2d[1], 0, "", stDetail2d[2], 3, "", stDetail2d[3], 2, "", stDetail2d[4], 1
y = y + add_Y endif endif
if iObjectType = TAP | iObjectType = SHOWER_TAP then ui_outfield `Тип 2D-символа`, x1, y, x4-x1-1, 15 if iObjectType = SHOWER_TAP then ui_infield{3} "TapSymbol", x4, y-4, cx, 20, 8, "", 4, 1, -x3-1, 20, -x3-1, 20, "", `Детальный`, `Детальный`, "", `Простой`, `Простой`, "", `Символический 1`, `Символический 1`, "", `Символический 2`, `Символический 2` else ui_infield{3} "TapSymbol", x4, y-4, cx, 20, 8, "", 2, 1, -x3-1, 20, -x3-1, 20, "", `Детальный`, `Детальный`, "", `Простой`, `Простой`, "", `Символический`, `Символический` endif y = y + add_Y endif
if iObjectType = MOP_SINK |\ iObjectType = SINK_BELFAST |\ iObjectType = SINK_CORNER |\ iObjectType = SINK_GENERAL then ui_outfield `Тип Символа Смесителя`, x1, y, x4-x1-1, 15 ui_infield{3} "TapSymbol", x4, y-4, cx, 20, 8, "", 2, 1, -x3-1, 20, -x3-1, 20, "", `Детальный`, `Детальный`, "", `Простой`, `Простой`, "", `Символический`, `Символический`, "", `Откл.`, `Откл.` y = y + add_Y endif ENDIF
if iObjectType = SHOWER_CABIN then ui_infield{3} "bOpenDoor2D", x1, y-3, 120, 20, 7, "", 2, 1, 20, 20, 20, 20, 0, `Дверь откр.в 2D`, 0, 1, `Дверь откр.в 2D`, 1 y = y + add_Y endif
cx = 40 UI_PICT 4, x1, y-3, 24,17, 1 ! ui_frame_pen_MEP.png UI_OUTFIELD `Перо Контура`, x2,y, x5-x2-cx-1,18 ! Contour Pen UI_INFIELD "gs_cont_pen", x5-cx,y-4, cx,22 y = y + add_Y
UI_PICT 3, x1, y-3, 13,17, 1 ! ui_fill_type_MEP.png
UI_OUTFIELD `Тип Штриховки`, x2,y, x3-x2,15, 0 ! Fill Type UI_INFIELD "gs_fill_type", x6,y+16, x3-x2,25 y = y + add_Y*2
cx = 40 UI_PICT 2, x1, y-3, 24,17, 1 ! ui_fill_pen_MEP.png
UI_OUTFIELD `Перо Штриховки`, x2,y, x5-x2-cx-1,18, 0 ! Fill Pen UI_INFIELD "gs_fill_pen", x5-cx,y-6, cx,23 y = y + add_Y
UI_PICT 1, x1, y-3, 24,17, 1 ! ui_back_pen_MEP.png
UI_OUTFIELD `Перо Фона Штриховки`, x2,y, x5-x2-cx-1,18, 0 ! Background Pen UI_INFIELD "gs_back_pen", x5-cx,y-6, cx,23 y = y + add_Y
if bEnableDashedLineType then UI_PICT "ui_contour_line_flat(1)", x1, y-3, 20, 20, 1
UI_OUTFIELD `Тип Штриховой Линии`, x2,y, x3-x2,15, 0 UI_INFIELD "gs_DashedLine", x6,y+16, x3-x2,27 y = y + add_Y endif
IF bEnableCenterlinePars THEN y = y + 5
UI_PICT 34, x1, y-2, 24,17, 1
UI_OUTFIELD `Тип Линии Оси`, x2,y, x3-x2,15, 0 ! Centerline Type UI_INFIELD "MEP_cline_type", x2,y+16, x3-x2,25 y = y + 19 + add_Y
cx = 40 UI_PICT 35, x1, y, 24,17, 1
UI_OUTFIELD `Перо Линии Оси`, x2,y+3, x3-x2-cx-1,18, 0 ! Centerline Pen UI_INFIELD "MEP_cline_pen", x3-cx,y, cx,22 y = y + add_Y ENDIF
x1 = 228 x2 = x1 + 18 x3 = x2 + 100 xEnd = 440 y = pageStartY - 3
UI_STYLE 0,1 UI_OUTFIELD `3D-отображение`, x1, y, xEnd-x1,18 ! --- 3D View --- y = y + 24 UI_STYLE 0, 0
IF bEnable3dDetail THEN UI_OUTFIELD `3D-детализация`, x1, y, x3-x1-1, 15 UI_INFIELD{3} "gs_detlevel_3D_m", x3, y-4, xEnd-x3-1, 20, 8, "", 2, 1, xEnd-x3-1, 20, xEnd-x3-1, 20, "", `Детальный`, 2, "", `Простой`, 1, "", `Упрощенный`, 3, "", `Откл.`, 0
y = y + 24 ENDIF
if bResol then UI_OUTFIELD `Аппроксимация`, x1, y, x3-x1-2, 13 UI_INFIELD "gs_resol", x3, y-4, xEnd-x3-1, 18 y = y + 24 ENDIF
if bEnableShadow then ui_infield{3} "gs_shadow", x1, y-3, xEnd-x1, 20, ! Shadow 7, "", 2, 1, 20, 20, 20, 20, 0, `Отбрасывание Теней`, 0, 1, `Отбрасывание Теней`, 1 y = y + 24 endif
IF bEnableUseSystemMat THEN stUseSysMat = " "+`Покрытие Системы` UI_INFIELD{3} "useSysMat", x1, y-3, xEnd-x1, 20, 7, "", 2, 1, 20, 20, 20, 20, 0, stUseSysMat, 0, 1, stUseSysMat, 1 y = y + 24 ENDIF
nMaterials = 0 for i = 1 TO vardim1(ui_matpar_names) if ui_matpar_names[i][2] <> "" then nMaterials = nMaterials + 1 next i
nMaterialRows = 9 - bEnable3dDetail - bResol - bEnableShadow - bEnableUseSystemMat
bOneRowMaterials = 1 if nMaterialRows >= (nMaterials * 2) then bOneRowMaterials = 0
bMoreMaterialOptions = 0 if nMaterials > nMaterialRows then bMoreMaterialOptions = 1
for i = 1 TO MIN(vardim1(ui_matpar_names), nMaterialRows) if ui_matpar_names[i][2] <> "" then bLocked = 0 if vardim1(ui_matpar_locked) >= i then bLocked = ui_matpar_locked[i] endif
if not(i = nMaterialRows and bMoreMaterialOptions) then if bLocked then ui_pict 5, x1, y-2, 12,17, 1 ! ui_mat_lock_MEP.png else ui_pict 6, x1, y-2, 12,17, 1 ! ui_mat_MEP.png endif endif
if bOneRowMaterials then if i = nMaterialRows and bMoreMaterialOptions then ui_style 1,0 ui_outfield `Доп. настройки Покрытий во вкладке Параметров`, x1, y, 20+xText+125, 15 ui_style 0,0 else xText = 71
matPlace = STRSTR(ui_matpar_names[i][1], " " + `Покрытие`) if matPlace > 0 then ui_matpar_names[i][1] = STRSUB(ui_matpar_names[i][1], 1, matPlace-1)
ui_outfield ui_matpar_names[i][1], x1 + 15, y, xText, 15, 4 * bLocked ui_infield ui_matpar_names[i][2], x1 + 20 + xText, y-4, 120, 23 y = y + 24 endif else ui_outfield ui_matpar_names[i][1] + " ", x1 + 18, y, xEnd-x1-31, 15, 4 * bLocked y = y + 24 ui_infield ui_matpar_names[i][2], x2, y-6, 195, 23 y = y + 24 endif endif next i
y = y + 2 + ui_3dviewpar_rowspace endif
! ---------- Appliance visualization tab ----------- if ui_appearance_type_m = 2 then UI_SEPARATOR 5, pageStartY + 135, 440, pageStartY + 135 UI_SEPARATOR 222, pageStartY + 140, 222, pageStartY + 225
x1 = 5 x2 = 120 x3 = 235 x4 = 360 x5 = 400 x6 = 440 yCurrent = pageStartY + 25 ui_style 0,0
ui_outfield `Перо Контура`, x3, yCurrent, x5-x3-2, 15 ui_infield "gs_cont_pen", x5, yCurrent-4, x6-x5, 22 yCurrent = yCurrent +27
ui_outfield `Тип Штриховки`, x3, yCurrent, x4-x3-2, 15 ui_infield "gs_fill_type", x4, yCurrent-4, x6-x4, 22 yCurrent = yCurrent +27
ui_outfield `Перо Штриховки`, x3, yCurrent, x5-x3-2, 15 ui_infield "gs_fill_pen", x5, yCurrent-4, x6-x5, 22 yCurrent = yCurrent +27
ui_outfield `Перо Фона`, x3, yCurrent, x5-x3-2, 15 ui_infield "gs_back_pen", x5, yCurrent-4, x6-x5, 22
if bEnableMaterials then UI_SEPARATOR 222, pageStartY, 222, pageStartY + 132
yCurrent = pageStartY
ui_style 0,1 ui_outfield `2D-отображение`, x3, yCurrent, x6-x3, 15 ui_outfield `Покрытия`, x1, yCurrent, 215-x1, 15 ui_style 0,0 yCurrent = pageStartY + 25
for i = 1 TO vardim1(ui_matpar_names) if ui_matpar_names[i][2] <> "" THEN ui_outfield ui_matpar_names[i][1], x1, yCurrent, x2-x1-2, 15 ui_infield ui_matpar_names[i][2], x2, yCurrent-4, 215-x2, 24 yCurrent = yCurrent +27 endif next i endif
yCurrent = pageStartY + 139
UI_STYLE 0,1 ui_outfield `Минимальное Пространство`, x3, yCurrent, x6-x3, 15 ui_outfield `3D-отображение`, x1, yCurrent, 215-x1, 15 ui_style 0,0 yCurrent = yCurrent +24
ui_outfield `Спереди`, x3, yCurrent, x4-x3-2, 15 ui_infield "MSFront", x4, yCurrent-4, x6-x4, 22 yCurrent = yCurrent +23
ui_outfield `Сбоку 1`, x3, yCurrent, x4-x3-2, 15 ui_infield "MSSide", x4, yCurrent-4, x6-x4, 22 yCurrent = yCurrent +23
ui_outfield `Сбоку 2`, x3, yCurrent, x4-x3-2, 15 ui_infield "MSSide2", x4, yCurrent-4, x6-x4, 22
yCurrent = pageStartY + 163
ui_outfield `3D`, x1, yCurrent, x2-x1-2, 15 ui_infield "gs_detlevel_3D", x2, yCurrent-4, 215-x2, 22 yCurrent = yCurrent +24
if bResol then UI_OUTFIELD `Аппроксимация`, x1, yCurrent, x2-x1-2, 13 UI_INFIELD "gs_resol", x2, yCurrent-4, 215-x2, 18 ENDIF
yCurrent = yCurrent +24
if bEnableShadow then ui_infield{3} "gs_shadow", x1, yCurrent-2, 215-x1, 15, ! Shadow 7, "", 2, 1, 20, 20, 20, 20, 0, `Отбрасывание Теней`, 0, 1, `Отбрасывание Теней`, 1 endif endif
